    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six engine with its factory-spec individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example has undergone a comprehensive mechanical validation, including a precision valve clearance adjustment and a complete VANOS system overhaul utilizing Beisan components. The high-pressure VANOS oil line and rod bearings have been addressed proactively. The chassis remains structurally pristine with documented subframe reinforcement. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a GKN variable M-differential, providing exceptional torque vectoring. The suspension maintains its factory kinematics with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, preserving the iconic 50/50 weight distribution. Finished in Titanium Silver over Nappa leather, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast seeking mechanical and aesthetic perfection.",
