    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a collector-grade vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster, enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found across the bodywork. The wheels are pristine, with no curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with deep tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The premium leather seating shows no signs of bolster wear or creasing, the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats, and the dashboard is free of any UV fading or rattles. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the climate control, functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history with every maintenance interval performed early at certified dealerships. The engine bay is concours-clean, and the undercarriage shows no signs of inclement weather exposure. This sale includes all original manuals, two master keys, and the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key example that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
